belka.mol

Class Assembly

  • java.lang.Object
    • belka.mol.Assembly
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public abstract class Assembly
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Abstract class describing behavior of an assembly. Assembly is the group of atoms, for example residue or nucleotide.
    Author:
    Alexej Abyzov
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
